further tell you that i would have made the same decision 
miss robinson said the newspaper staff offered to edit the story 
to satisfy smith but the offer was rejected he also rejected a 
request to run a blank space or the word censored in place of 
the story 
although miss dixon has worried the school officials will bar 
her from giving her valedictory address on graduation night june 
10 ms raymond said she will be allowed to speak and participate 
