many japanese workers transferring to 
their companies us branches have a problem american schools 
dont prepare their children for the tough competition to get into 
a japanese university 
japans solution and a testament to the growing japanese 
presence in this country is tennessee meiji gakuin high school 
which will be the first fully accredited japanese high school in 
