grown for semiconductors electronic parts used in computers and 
other devices blagov said 
one reason for putting mir on automatic mode is to give a rest 
to its support staff at mission control and tracking stations that 
have been working continuously for three years blagov said 
people are tired they havent had vacations we owe them 
this he said 
